Install Python and pip. (python3 get-pip.py)
Install requests, time and yaml modules. (pip install requests, pip install pyyaml)
Add yaml file or change the code in input.yaml file to list out endpoint inputs.
Run program. Give yaml input file and interval for health check as arguments. (e.g. python3 main.py input.yaml 15)
This will log domain wise availability percentage every 15 seconds.
